BT 1 0 0 1 0 51 Tm /F1 9 Tf 12 TL (This paper provides the theoretical mechanism missing from all prior work: why 40 Hz specifically. The answer is the Wike) Tj T* (Coherence Law. 40 Hz external entrainment forces gamma_eff below gamma_c in the hippocampal-entorhinal network --) Tj T* (the same network where Bootstrap Nucleation failure \(Paper 21\) begins in Alzheimer's disease. The 40 Hz stimulus is a) Tj T* (Bootstrap restart from outside the system. It does not treat the plaques. It restores the coherence that was lost before the) Tj T* (plaques became dominant. The treatment and the measurement are the same channel.) Tj T* ET
